{
  "stem": "17301.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 464.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And they came, and they actually-- it wasn't even that much up to me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "It was up to them to select us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "So they selected, thank god, the three of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And they took us to a large barn, and we didn't know what to expect.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "And there were people sitting at a table with-- like a small, a small table, a chair and a small table.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "And they had a needle in their hands, and we had no idea what was-- what was the needle for.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "Until they said, now you-- we're going to give you a number, so that we can keep-- you know, we know where you are, and who are.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "And we had to give them our name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "And then they-- they gave us the tattoo.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "They tattoos us, all three of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember my mother crying and my sister was crying very, very bitterly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said to them, you know something?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I says, you know, don't cry that hard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, don't cry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the reason that they gave you a number is probably because they're gonna keep track of you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe, you know, if we have a number, maybe we're gonna be working, and that-- maybe that is a good sign.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So, that's kind of, you know, my mother realized that maybe I was right.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was our first day of having a tattoo on our arms.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we got tattoos, consecutive numbers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What numbers were they?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The numbers were 6731, 6732, and 6733, which I have the 6733.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Those were the numbers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After that, the following day they collected 250 women from our barrack, who had the numbers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took us away to a different place, which-- ooh-- happened to be called the Brzezinka.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
